data.description: !!!!Price Reduction!!!!. SELLER PAYS $3,000.00 OF BUYER'S CONCESSIONS WITH FULL PRICE OFFER! OWN YOUR HOME THIS 2024.  Embrace the comfort and elegance of this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence with 2 additional rooms that can be CONVERTED into a 4-5 BEDROOM home or a HOME OFFICE.  Over 2,000 sq ft of thoughtfully upgraded living space with TILE throughout. As you step inside, be captivated by the vaulted ceilings in the main areas.  Each space is bathed in natural light, accentuated by charming PLANTATION SHUTTERS.  The heart of the home is the exquisitely upgraded kitchen, seamlessly flowing into the expansive living and dining area and upgraded BATHROOMS. This open-concept design ensures every moment is spent in style and comfort. Admire the beautiful pool views through the elegant double French doors, inviting you to explore the outdoor oasis.  Retreat to the luxurious master bedroom, featuring a trendy barn door that opens to a beautiful en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms, situated opposite the master suite, offer privacy and tranquility.  Step outside to your personal paradise: a lanai opening to an in-ground saltwater POOL, equipped with an automatic switch and solar heating for year-round enjoyment. Enjoy the outside BBQ area to entertain family and friends. The delightful fruit trees and ambient lighting create the perfect setting for memorable gatherings.  Privacy and security are paramount, assured by the enclosing fence with keyed locks and the option to activate an ADT security system.  **Roof 5 years old**, **Water Heater 2 years old**.  This home isn't just a place to live; it's a lifestyle waiting for you. Act quickly and schedule your showing today — this extraordinary opportunity won't last long.  This property has everything you are looking for.  You could own this home for the same amount of money you are paying for rent.  VERY CLOSE TO DISNEY THEME PARKS, Shopping, Universities and main highways.  Schedule your showing today.  Bring your offer.  Don't wait. This home is move in ready condition.
